caption:
I just turned 49 years old with this guy by my side through all of life’s storms

We just came out of one and I know we will eventually go into another one. Christ is our firm foundation and we will get through. 

I don’t care what you hear or see on the internet, find someone who tells you to focus on Jesus and never let go. 

Though one may be overpowered,
two can defend themselves.

A cord of three strands is not quickly broken.

#marriageisablessing #holymatrimony
